title: Pixel 5G Import from USA to Dubai
content:
Hi,

I want to buy Pixel 5G from USA to Dubai.

I can see there are 2 version showing :

GD1YQ (US)                             mmWave & Sub-6
GTT9Q/G5NZ6 (non-US)       Sub-6

I can see mmWave is available in USA only, while Sub-6 is used by somany countries.

Now, if I buy US version and use it in Dubai or when I travel to Australia then this Sub-6 5G will support or not. In Dubai and Australia both service provider using Sub-6.

This US version have 2 sim - 1main SIM and another e-SIM ?

I heard that US version is locked, so just want to make sure its Unlocked and support both mmWare and Sub-6 in major Countries.

I'm aware about support and warranty not get in Dubai, but I'm ok with that.

Please anyone know about this, help me.
